  "title": "Facilities and Maintenance Technician (Automotive / 5.25 days) [EL]",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Conduct routine inspections and maintenance of facilities, including electrical systems, air-conditioning, compressed air, and chilled-water systems.</li>\n  <li>Coordinate with contractors for routine servicing and emergency repairs to ensure uninterrupted building operations.</li>\n  <li>Supervise vendors during renovation projects to ensure a seamless transition to newly updated areas.</li>\n  <li>Maintain cleanliness and good housekeeping in areas such as the AHU and switch rooms to keep equipment and facilities in optimal condition.</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with contractors and vendors to execute schedules, ensuring cost-effective and high-quality repairs and renovations.</li>\n  <li>Perform hands-on repairs for plumbing, sanitary systems, electrical, and general building maintenance.</li>\n  <li>Conduct basic troubleshooting for telephone line issues.</li>\n  <li>Undertake any additional duties as assigned from time to time.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>",
